## Proposed Changes

### Phase 1: Core Models

All new models will live in `Backend/src/core/payments/models/`.

---

#### [NEW] [payment.model.js](file:///c:/Users/SHUBHAM/Desktop/AppZeto-Master-Product-/Backend/src/core/payments/models/payment.model.js)

Adapted from the user's spec. Changes from the provided schema:
- `gateway` made optional (COD/wallet payments have no gateway)
- Added `module` field (`food`, `dining`, etc.) for multi-module support
- Collection: `payments`

```js
// Fields: orderId, userId, amount, currency, method (card/upi/netbanking/wallet/cod),
//         gateway (razorpay/stripe/paypal - optional), gatewayOrderId, gatewayPaymentId,
//         status (created/pending/success/failed/refunded), rawResponse, module
```

---

#### [NEW] [transaction.model.js](file:///c:/Users/SHUBHAM/Desktop/AppZeto-Master-Product-/Backend/src/core/payments/models/transaction.model.js)

Universal ledger. Changes from the provided schema:
- Added `module` field for scoping
- `balanceAfter` computed atomically during wallet update
- Collection: `transactions`

```js
// Fields: orderId, paymentId, entityType (user/restaurant/deliveryBoy/admin),
//         entityId, type (credit/debit), amount, balanceAfter, status, description
```

---

#### [NEW] [wallet.model.js](file:///c:/Users/SHUBHAM/Desktop/AppZeto-Master-Product-/Backend/src/core/payments/models/wallet.model.js)

Replaces the entity-specific `FoodUserWallet` with a universal wallet. Changes:
- Supports all entity types (user, restaurant, deliveryBoy, admin)
- `lockedAmount` for pending settlements
- Unique compound index on [(entityId, entityType)](file:///c:/Users/SHUBHAM/Desktop/AppZeto-Master-Product-/Frontend/src/modules/Food/pages/user/cart/Cart.jsx#78-2855)
- Collection: `wallets`

```js
// Fields: entityType, entityId, balance, lockedAmount
```

---

#### [NEW] [settlement.model.js](file:///c:/Users/SHUBHAM/Desktop/AppZeto-Master-Product-/Backend/src/core/payments/models/settlement.model.js)

For restaurant/delivery partner payouts. Collection: `settlements`

```js
// Fields: entityType (restaurant/deliveryBoy), entityId, amount,
//         transactions[], status (pending/processing/processed/failed),
//         payoutId, processedAt
```

---

#### [NEW] [refund.model.js](file:///c:/Users/SHUBHAM/Desktop/AppZeto-Master-Product-/Backend/src/core/payments/models/refund.model.js)

For tracking refunds. Collection: `refunds`

```js
